condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :PA Annex A to Schedule A (Subsidiary Loan Agreement) Para 8 | Description :FCIC send Bank not later than 6-mosafter end of each FY, certified copies of the records and accounts audited accounts, and an opinion on such records and accounts bythe auditors. | Due Date :30-Jun-2011

Finance Agreement :PA Section I, C Para 3 (a) | Description :Fenghua City to carry out the dam safety remedial works and scheduleset out in the Hengshan Reservoir Report, satisfactory to the Bank. | Due Date :01-Jul-2011

Finance Agreement :PA Section I, C Para 3 (b) | Description :Fenghua City provide, by June 30, 2010, a revised O&M Plan for theHengshan Reservoir Dam, based on the comments offered by the Bank, and thereafter implement said plan accepted by the Bank. | DueDate :30-Jun-2010

Finance Agreement :PA Section I, C Para 3 (c) | Description :Fenghua City to provide, by Jun 30, 2010, a revised EmergencyPreparedness Plan for the Hengshan Reservoir Dam, based on the comments from the Bank, and implement said plan accepted by theBank. | Due Date :30-Jun-2010

Finance Agreement :PA Section IV, Para 10 | Description :Ningbo to cause Fenghua to pay a fee to FCIC to cover its admin cost anddebt ser obligation related to the Chunhu Town Infra Deve component and to vest ownership of assets in FCIC for 30 years. | DueDate :15-Feb-2014

Finance Agreement :PA Section IV, Para 7 (a) | Description :Fenghua City to prepare and submit to WB by Aug 15 yearly, starting2012, a proposed annual budget & financing plan for O&M of infras. constructed for Chunhu town. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Section IV, Para 8 (a) | Description :Fenghua City to require operators of WS syst. in Fenghua and WW mgtsystem in Chunhu Town to have their F/S audited each year and send to Fenghua no later than 6 mos after end of FY. | Frequency:Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Section IV, Para 8 (b) | Description :Fenghua (FH) send Bank each Sept starting 2013, annual report on WSsyst in FH & WW mgt syst in Chunhu to show if total rev are more than total op exp & the amt debt service exceeds the depr. |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Section IV, Para 9 (a) | Description :Fenghua send Bank a plan for levying and collecting ww user charges inChunhu Town to generate sufficient rev by Dec 31, 2016 to cover the cost of O&M the services (excl the cost of debt serv | Due Date:15-Feb-2014

Finance Agreement :PA Section IV, Para 9 (b) | Description :Fenghua send the Bank a plan for levying and coll WS charges in FHcoastal area to genr suff rev by: 12-31-2016 to cover the cost of O&M excl debt service cost (DSC) and 12-31-2022 | Due Date:15-Feb-2014
